prompts.frontCover: A humorous watercolor painting of three cartoon-style dogs of different breeds (a scruffy terrier, a goofy golden retriever, and a stout bulldog) sitting in a wonky, lopsided stack, one on top of the other, trying to look over a fence. The top dog is precariously balanced, paws flailing slightly, with a party hat askew on its head. The bottom dog looks squashed but determined. Splatters of muddy paw prints are artfully scattered around the bottom corners. In the center, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, the words "hope your birthday is a total riot". The artwork is a flat 2D design with soft flowing colors, visible paper texture, organic paint bleeds, and artistic brush strokes characteristic of a charming watercolor painting.
